    "The RF model obtained the highest accuracy, sensitivity, F1 score, AUROC, and AUPRC.",
    "The NN with attention model provided the highest specificity and precision but gave a relatively low sensitivity.",
    "The CNN and the proposed RF models had comparable AUROC performance, with an AUROC of 0.96 and 0.97, respectively.",
    "In summary, the RF model was optimal with an accuracy of 0.90, sensitivity of 0.96, specificity of 0.87, precision of 0.83, F1 score of 0.89, AUROC of 0.97, and AUPR of 0.95.",
    "The performance calculated with stratified tenfold cross validation are illustrated in Fig. 4c, d. All values are average scores of tenfold."
